listing.description:
Quality 4 bedroom detached bungalow with a number of outbuildings and detached workshop comes to the market in a prime location on the outskirts of Castlerea town centre.

The Property is finished to a good standard throughout with ample space around the property with a separate entrance to the workshop and outbuildings.
The property can also be divided into a 3 bedroom and a 1 bedroom en-suite self contained property with its own kitchen/dining and separate entrance door for access.

2 minutes drive to Castlerea town centre, 25 minutes drive to Roscommon town and 20 minutes drive to Knock Airport.

Early viewing advised to avoid disappointment.

Accommodation comprises 

Entrance hall 16.01 x 5.11 tiled floor 

Inner hall 30.06 x 3.04 tiled floor, storage presses. 

Sitting room 16.03 x 12.06 solid oak flooring, open fireplace with tiled surround, hearth and timber mantle, fitted curtains & centre piece light as feature. 

Living room 14.02 x 9.09 solid oak flooring, open fireplace with mahogany surround, marble inset and hearth, fitted curtains. 

Kitchen/dining 14.01 x 9.10 fitted units with tiled floor and tiled between units, hotpress/storage with solid timber door to garden.

Bed 1: 13.08 x 10.09 fitted built-in wardrobe, carpet and curtains. 

Bed 2: 13.09 x 11.09 solid oak flooring, fitted built-in wardrobe and fitted curtains. 

Bed 3: 13.09 x 9.11 fitted carpet, built in wardrobes, fitted curtains. 

Bed 4: 9.01 x 8.09 fitted carpet and curtains, shower room off, wc, whb, electric shower fully tiled floor and walls. 

Utility/kitchen 12.05 x 12.01 fitted units, plumbed for appliances, lino flooring, walkin pantry. 

Main bathroom 9.11 x 6.03 white suite, mounted wall unit over sink, tiled floor and half tiled walls, separate electric shower fully tiled.

Outside block boundary wall to front sides and rear of property with mature gardens to front and rear, separate double gated entrance to side of property which leads to workshop and a range of outbuildings. 

Double garage 33.05 x 20.12 concrete floor, enclosed double storage shed with large roller door.

Fuel shed with large entrance door 20.11 x 14.01 concrete floor, esb, oil boiler. 

Large storage shed 20.11 x 14.01 concrete floor 

General oil fired central heating, open fireplace, septic tank, self contained 1 bedroom en-suite ideal for a granny flat. 2 minutes drive to Castlerea town centre.

Viewing comes highly recommended by the sole agent and strictly by appointment only Contact Nigel Dineen MIPAV MMCEPI Auctioneers Roscommon 

Everything we touch turns to SOLD
